Detailed Description

template<class ITERATOR>
class GnuPlotDump::gp_dumper< ITERATOR >

Iterator dumper.

<br /> Class for dumping stuff to mc2dbg8 etc. Needed since they are defined as if ( false ) Use like so: mc2dbg << it_dump( cont.begin(), cont.end(), ",") << endl;
